Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.99,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs17}室外\N野營\N登山用品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:11.41,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(460,312)\fad(0,3)}Schlaf是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是登山道具店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是寶山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有便攜小鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈦製的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好輕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schlaf是指睡袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  要7萬円
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼輕便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高挑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我是一個學校的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我點建議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個1萬8千円的睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個2萬4千円的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪個比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:00:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實際上是準備帶著帳篷和睡袋去「縱走」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「縱走」？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一邊露營一邊攀登幾座山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是現在正猶豫要買哪個睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是重量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.91,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}化學纖維製\N重\N體積大\N便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要背一整天所以重量很關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:22.07,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}羽絨製\N輕\N便攜\N高價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然打工攢了不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣一來預算就很吃緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在猶豫也就意味著其實想要貴的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼回答才能讓她滿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其放棄並妥協
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得就算會後悔還是不妥協比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  謝謝你推了我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去結帳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也登山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一瞬間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就這麼回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就是山友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換一下郵箱地址吧  我叫齊藤楓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向  我啊  其實很不擅長和人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  事到如今還說這個做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得這麼乾脆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你自己注意到了這不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,80)\fs21\frz-19}上次多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  是楓同學發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又交到了一個朋友
